lead_paragraph: The Council election passed off quietly. The following Whigs were elected-Malcom W. Mearis, Wm. H. Young, Wm. W. Wilson, Charles Z. Lucas, Dr. J.H. Thomas, T, Whelan, Henry P.Brooks, John F. Daivs, Isaac Mules, Democrats-Adam Hornye, David Blamcord, Wm. H. Shelly, John Dukehart, G. D. Tewksbury, N. J. Dushane, Rouben S. Bowie, Wm.E. Beale, John S, Brwon. The Whigs gain one. Tell, Abell,

headline.main: Baltimore Council Election--Reported Removal of Consul Owen--Release of the Pampero..
